                    <h6 class="mt-4">Fire Survival Tips</h6>
                    <ul class="list-group mt-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Stay low to the ground to avoid smoke inhalation.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">If trapped inside, close all doors and use a cloth to block smoke from entering.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Don't use elevators during a fire.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">If possible, use a fire extinguisher for small fires, but donâ€™t risk your safety.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Always have an emergency exit plan and stay calm.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h6 class="mt-4">Flood Survival Tips</h6>
                    <ul class="list-group mt-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Move to higher ground immediately.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">If trapped, climb to a rooftop or stay in a safe location until help arrives.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Do not walk or drive through floodwaters as they can be dangerous.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Listen to weather alerts and evacuation orders.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Keep emergency supplies such as water, food, and first aid kits on hand.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h6 class="mt-4">Earthquake Survival Tips</h6>
                    <ul class="list-group mt-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">If inside, take cover under a table or desk. Protect your head and neck.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">If outside, move to an open area away from buildings, trees, and power lines.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Stay away from windows and anything that could fall during aftershocks.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Check for hazards such as gas leaks or fires after the shaking stops.</li>
                    </ul>

                    <h6 class="mt-4">Landslide Survival Tips</h6>
                    <ul class="list-group mt-3">
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">If you are near a hill or mountain, move to an open space immediately.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">If trapped, create a barrier to protect yourself from debris.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Listen for warnings and evacuate immediately if instructed.</li>
                        <li class="list-group-item bg-transparent">Stay away from riverbeds and low-lying areas that might be affected.</li>
                    </ul>

